{"tid":1306780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭推逃犯條例社會幾經折騰  陳茂波籲珍惜眼前人","createTime":"2019-07-11T09:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T09:42:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78e32883ed1b80fa0b83f8450a51cf9a5e35b07f","tid":1306780,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"反送中運動期間有多名年輕人輕生。財政司司長陳茂波今日發表網誌，提及過去一個月社會幾經折騰，不少人感到情緒鬱悶。他呼籲大眾「珍惜眼前人、珍惜生命」。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波網誌以〈社情民意〉為題，指過去一個月社會幾經折騰，不少人感到身心疲累、情緒鬱悶，社會繃緊的氣氛留下待修復的傷痕：「無論如何，爭議過後最需要是相互溝通，尋求理解與出路。而無論分歧有多大，我相信有一點大家是有共識的：珍惜眼前人、珍惜生命。」<br />\n<br />\n他又指經過這段日子的波動，政府已認識到須改善機制，建立與市民更好的互動渠道，更好的聆聽和尊重市民的心聲，並且在決策過程中更多吸納市民的意見。他希望隨著施政改善，未來可逐步修補公眾與政府之間的嫌隙，重建彼此間的信任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E7%B1%B2%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%9C%BC%E5%89%8D%E4%BA%BA-%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD-%E7%9B%BC%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%96%93%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8527tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=32a7de93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&h=f23494d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E7%B1%B2%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%9C%BC%E5%89%8D%E4%BA%BA-%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD-%E7%9B%BC%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%96%93%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB/</a>"},{"pid":"b29e9e9f0d58a6411d646e8083488f297a0e3f29","tid":1306780,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:38:06.000Z","msg":"佢就嚟死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19645fb196da7fd0d34d321373befa9a18e133be","tid":1306780,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"又係得個講字"},{"pid":"b999cee0ac66e5e29abefafe19be6f36eb192a7f","tid":1306780,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"爭議過後？？？<br />\n<br />\n未完嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6b1a925a9074407740bc60b53a2d7444721a0d","tid":1306780,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為佢叫我地珍惜林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}